  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The Iburi clan has a unique talent of manifesting Smoke Release, an augmentative release that improves the area of effect of fire, and its destructive capabilities. Starting at 7th level, when you cast a jutsu with the Fire Release Keyword, you can give affected creatures a -2 penalty to one saving throw against the jutsu or your Will-O-Wisps feature.</p><p>Beginning at 15th level, twice per long rest, when you deal Fire damage, you automatically blind all affected creatures until the end of each of their turns.</p>",
